import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['yield'] = pd.to_numeric(data['yield'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['yield'])
    data = data.groupby(['variety'])['yield'].mean().reset_index()
    chart = sns.barplot(x='variety', y='yield', data=data)
    chart.axhline(y=data['yield'].max(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Max Yield: {data['yield'].max():.2f}")
    chart.axhline(y=data['yield'].min(), color='green', linestyle='--', label=f"Min Yield: {data['yield'].min():.2f}")
    chart.legend()
    return chart

chart = plot(data)
